    "data": [
        {
            "title": "旺角MMA｜綠衣男路權問題拍打的士兼吐口水 的哥扭鬥至眼鏡波鞋飛脫",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"旺角MMA｜綠衣男路權問題拍打的士兼吐口水 的哥扭鬥至眼鏡波鞋飛脫\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/38feb8b5b508d66e05ddb06e8f1e5e3d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021909562239332.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">旺角MMA｜綠衣男路權問題拍打的士兼吐口水 的哥扭鬥至眼鏡波鞋飛脫</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>昨日（18日）網上流傳兩段影片，一名綠衣男途人與一名的士司機在旺角豉油街街頭拉扯及扭鬥地上，其間的士司機眼鏡和波鞋飛脫，須送往廣華醫院醫治，綠衣男則在警員抵達前離開現場。警方指，33歲姓梁的士男司機遭一名年約20歲男途人拳打，案件列作「襲擊致造成身體傷害」跟進，暫未有人被捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>事件發生在周二晚上8時許，據悉，綠衣男當時與一名女性友人，在豉油街50號富達大廈對開準備過馬路，影片中的的哥駕着的士險與二人相撞，綠衣男怒拍的士車頭蓋，的士司機落車激烈理論，期間綠衣男一度向對方「放飛劍」吐口水，結果口角釀成武鬥。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089441/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"從網上一段影片可見，兩人在街頭拉扯， 的哥拉住綠衣男的手，期間有人叫道：「報警，報警，報警」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3829ae3d10e52bfbbb5c4e701bbf125/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_03_13_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        從網上一段影片可見，兩人在街頭拉扯， 的哥拉住綠衣男的手，期間有人叫道：「報警，報警，報警」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089442/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"綠衣男極力掙扎，與對方形成拔河之勢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/79bbeb5c6e95761cfd6d3045d7d5ce7c/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_03_24_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        綠衣男極力掙扎，與對方形成拔河之勢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089443/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"同行女友人則拉住他的衫角勸交。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41f3e89754e37bc15a6a7fc77d3514ca/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_08_22_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        同行女友人則拉住他的衫角勸交。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089444/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"同行女友人則拉住他的衫角勸交，但無果，大批途人被這一幕吸引，駐足觀看。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/63aea9d1c4a2a76fe9710a8b41740831/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_09_11_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        同行女友人則拉住他的衫角勸交，但無果，大批途人被這一幕吸引，駐足觀看。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089445/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名穿灰色上衣的男子走近，大叫「唔該你駛埋架車先啦！」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ab72109d43b5a6e75aeab8c4dc4f888f/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_10_23_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名穿灰色上衣的男子走近，大叫「唔該你駛埋架車先啦！」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>從網上一段影片可見，兩人在街頭拉扯， 的哥拉住綠衣男的手，期間有人叫道：「報警，報警，報警」，綠衣男極力掙扎，雙方形成拔河之勢，同行女友人則拉住他的衫角勸交但無果，大批途人被這一幕吸引，駐足觀看。\n\n</p>\n<p>由於的士停在馬路中心，阻礙交通，一名穿灰色上衣的男子忍不住走近二人，叫道：「唔該你駛埋架車先啦！」的士司機稍一分神，綠衣男以右手手肘推了的士司機胸口一下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089446/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"另一影片鏡頭一轉，只見二人已跌坐地上扭作一團，的哥雙腳波鞋甩掉，眼鏡亦飛脫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32ae016990de6f8cc6ec2ff7c86d5d69/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_9_58_24_PM_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        另一影片鏡頭一轉，只見二人已跌坐地上扭作一團，的哥雙腳波鞋甩掉，眼鏡亦飛脫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089447/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的哥從後死抱着綠衣男不放。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0429579de7c7f74fc97ce356e153b964/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_17_42_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的哥從後死抱着綠衣男不放。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089448/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"綠衣男則嘗試拉開對方的手，然後側身以手肘撐地。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3553e0a799cc48c6b00bcd2d619fcd3/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_18_19_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        綠衣男則嘗試拉開對方的手，然後側身以手肘撐地。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089449/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dbeccd15363a33acb2d648805fdd9ff9/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_18_45_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089450/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"成功脫身並站起。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7430f06b8249b885b2fb2fee900b0743/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_19_05_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        成功脫身並站起。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089451/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士司機隨即拾回眼鏡。片段至此結束。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/085a8b53ebbe1ff1d16f58f39540d8bc/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_19_24_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士司機隨即拾回眼鏡。片段至此結束。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>另一影片鏡頭一轉，只見二人已跌坐地上扭作一團，的哥雙腳波鞋甩掉，眼鏡亦飛脫，從後死抱着綠衣男不放，綠衣男則嘗試脫身，他以手肘撐地用力，成功掙脫站起，的士司機未有追擊下去，只是站起來拾回眼鏡。影片在此結束。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089458/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27eaff1925999a8fc53c2542690269a0/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_28_20_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4089459/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"二人打鬥的地點旺角豉油街街頭。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/134ef09f4e0786762c11252f6ccb93f6/2025-02/Screenshot_2025-02-18_at_10_28_11_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人打鬥的地點旺角豉油街街頭。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方表示，18日晚約8時11分，接獲多人報案，指兩名男子在旺角豉油街50號對開打鬥，有人報稱男性友人被的士司機毆打，亦有人指兩人是互毆。涉事的哥則報案稱，自己被一名男子拳打。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方指，經調查，相信涉事的士本沿着豉油街往洗衣街方向行駛，其間因過路權問題，與一名年約20歲、短髮男途人爭執，並遭拳打，手腳擦傷及感胸口痛，由救護車送廣華醫院治理。警方將案件列作「襲擊致造成身體傷害」，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
